<html>
<head>
    <style>
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .otp-container {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .otp-code {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <h1>Hello {{name}},</h1>
    <p>Your OTP for verification is:</p>
    <div class="otp-container">
        <div class="otp-code">{{otp}}</div>
    </div>
    <p>This OTP will expire in 5 minutes.</p>
    <p>If you didn't request this OTP, please ignore this email.</p>
    <p>Thanks,<br>Your App Team</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>